name: complex_if_mul_common_left_factor
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Multiplying a common left operand across an if expression must choose branchwise products.
law: (= (fuzz-mul {common} (if {cond} {a} {b})) (if {cond} (fuzz-mul {common} {a}) (fuzz-mul {common} {b})))
